messages: I wouldn't bother with the length check, your function will traverse both lists twice
if you can order the elements, then you can get O(n log n) algorithms very easily
I don't know how to write one nicely, but it may well be worth it to pick up a factor of n/log n
obviously it isn't a good idea to write a dozen different versions of every command such as ls or grep
